    <item>
      <title>Getting Started</title>
      <link>https://alias-bitsignal.github.io/bismuthcoin/docs/getting-started/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://alias-bitsignal.github.io/bismuthcoin/docs/getting-started/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;This guide will help you quickly get started with &lt;strong&gt;BISMUTH&lt;/strong&gt; as a &lt;strong&gt;regular user&lt;/strong&gt;, as a &lt;strong&gt;developer&lt;/strong&gt; or as an &lt;strong&gt;exchange&lt;/strong&gt; planning on implementing a $BIS trading pair.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;User Guideline&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;user-guideline&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#user-guideline&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start with a &lt;a href=&#34;https://alias-bitsignal.github.io/bismuthcoin/wallet/&#34; &gt;Bismuth Wallet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get familiar with the different available address schemes (rsa, ecdsa, &amp;hellip;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get some $BIS from an exchange or ask on the discord server for a faucet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do low value test transactions to learn sending/ receiving $BIS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check your transaction on the &lt;a href=&#34;https://bismuth.im/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Bismuth Explorer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirmations before respending: 1&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
