&lt;li&gt;Read the Whitepaper&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install the Bismuth Mainnet Node&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Study the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bismuthfoundation/TornadoWallet/tree/master/wallet/crystals&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Tornado Wallet Apps&lt;/a&gt; to learn how to extend the Mainnet node&lt;/li&gt;
