&lt;li&gt;Bismuth &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bismuthfoundation/BismuthAPI/blob/master/Doc/commands_reference.md&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Native API&lt;/a&gt; command reference&lt;/li&gt;
